title: My "Go The Fuck To Sleep" Playlist.
description:
This is the playlist that I listen to when I go to sleep. 

This torrent WILL appear in your client as "go The Fuck To Sleep". don't be worried. That's just what I saved the folder as. 



Here's the tracks on it:

2. Of Mice & Men - When You Can't Sleep At Night

42. Half Life 2 OST - Path of Borealis
43. Tokio Hotel - World Behind My Wall (Acoustic
44. Van Canto - Last Night of the Kings
45. 30 Seconds To Mars - The Story (acoustic)

I couldn't figure out how the fuck to make a .m3u file. So I came up with a more entertaining way for tumblr to do it.

1. Go into iTunes
2. Right click the bar at the top that has all the things you can sort things by and turn on "comments". 
3. Search "Come on cutie gimme da booty"
4. Each song will have a number after it. This is the order in the playlist it should go. 
5. If you click "comments" at the top of the screen it will organize it by number for you. 
6. Select all, drag in to playlist
7. Go The Fuck To Sleep. 



I'm uploading this here because I'm Zoey_Redbird, and my main account is used for discographies and I didn't want this to ruin it. Enjoy if you want it, fuck off if you don't. 

I love you all. Have fun sleeping.
